aracters to cars to animals. Start a relax game with easy mode and challenge yourself all the way to hard mode created for hardcore puzzle fans. Finally have fun playing the game in eye-catching environments designed to immerse you in the gameplay.", "short_description": "For the first time ever, you can enjoy playing jigsaw puzzle in real 3D and in VR. Jigsaw Puzzle VR is a highly appealing game for every gender and age and a real catch for jigsaw puzzle fans. Enjoy playing 25 different puzzles from fantasy characters to cars to animals. Start a relax game with easy mode and challenge yourself all the way to hard mode created for hardcore puzzle fans. Finally have fun playing the game in eye-catching environments designed to immerse you in the gameplay."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "http://riseangle.com/games/jigsaw-puzzle-vr/jigsaw-puzzle-vr-privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "http://riseangle.com/games/jigsaw-puzzle-vr/terms-of-service", "publisher_name": "RiseAngle, Inc.", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "http://riseangle.com/games/jigsaw-puzzle-vr", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": null, "context_topics": [], "external_subscription_type": null, "genres": ["ADVENTURE", "CASUAL", "EDUCATIONAL", "PUZZLE", "SIMULATION"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": null, "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["TOUCHPAD"], "supported_player_modes": [], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "648796216321020"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 11, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "201811217220343"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1994392700831844"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "554507911590991"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1679208025532958"}, {"sta